 > Describe the architecture                                                    
▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀

 ● The system has three layers:

   1. Frontend
     • React components
     • State management
     • Routing
   • Backend
     • REST API
     • Authentication
     • Database access
   • Infrastructure
     • Docker containers
     • CI/CD pipeline
                                                                                
